did.head: DESCRIPTIVE SUMMARY
did.unittitle: ILR School Dean's Office Additional Files, 1966-1985
did.repository: Kheel Center for Labor-Management Documentation and Archives, Cornell University Library
did.abstract: School administration files, building files, extension files, fiscal files, correspondence, legislation files, publication lists and research development files are included in this collection.

scopecontent.head: COLLECTION DESCRIPTION
scopecontent.p: Records are filed according to the Records Retention Schedule codes:
A-1 through A-26: School administrative files.
M-1 through M-32: Institutes and Conferences.
ST-1 through ST-10: Undergraduate student education files.
ST-19 through ST26: Graduate student education files.
ST-39 through ST-51: Schedules and Program Planning.
